latestIgtvVideos.title: I got vaccinated & vlogged it ! 💯
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
FAQs & important info :

1. Which vaccine did I get? Covishield, Covaxin is less in stock and was available for 45+ second doses

2. Center? Surya Hospital, Santa Cruz, Mumbai

3. Did it hurt? As much as a mosquito bite. Was over in 10 seconds.

4. Was there social distancing? Most people here came in groups, so not exactly, but it's up to you to maintain it and keep your distance. I felt quite safe.

5. Cost? 1000 bucks

6. What to carry? Aadhar card, photo ID registered on Cowin, pen to fill the form, cash preferably to avoid touching card machine, water, some food/chocolate if you feel dizzy, sanitizer, sanitizer spray, extra mask. Water was provided at my center. 

7. What to wear? An 95 mask, and a cloth mask on top. Sleeveless/short sleeved clothing. Be comfortable as you have to wait there for 30 mins post the jab. You can wear gloves, face shield if you want, I didn't.

8. Where's your vaccination photo? I wasn't allowed to take any photos while inside the vaccination room. They had a lot of people to do and I was inside for exactly 30 seconds.

9. How to get an appointment? Please register yourself on Cowin & Aarogya Setu, activate alerts on Paytm app and Telegram channels to be notified of slots. Be patient, everyone will get it.

10. Side effects? No fever or cold, mild to severe body ache on following days and disrupted sleep and food habits. Normal 

11. Please encourage everyone to get vaccinated, especially 45+ year olds as the slots are available all the time. 

12. I'm sharing my experience so it can benefit someone and ease your tension, if any. Please share with whoever you think needs this.

13. I'm so so so grateful that I could get it. Please get yours as soon as you can 🙂

Ask me any additional questions in the comments and I'll answer! ♥️
